asset.hookText: http://www.skis.com/Icelantic-Nomad-RKR-Skis-2013/273566P,default,pd.html  The Icelantic Nomad RKR is a perfect ski if you are crashing in a Subaru, in a sleeping bag covered in husky fur. At 105mm underfoot, it can wonder in deep pow stashes with ease, and is super maneuverable in any type of terrain. The rocker, camber, rocker profile, adds some playfulness to hit any jibs or airs you can find, as you meander your way to the base area or trail head. If you don't know where you will be skiing or what conditions the day will have in store for you, and you want the right ski for any day, the Icelantic Nomad RKR will be at home under your boots.
